annotation.text:
MMS Meeting Reminders
Process Model is used to send reminders in News Tab, Also provides a task to meeting organizor about review the reminder.
Timer Node waits for Reminder Time. And flow forwards based on reminder time and review reminder field
Review Reminder Task is enabled if user selects enable review reminder field. This node collects the entry information from user

Post System Event To feed will post new entry in News Tab about the meeting reminder.
Deactive Old feed details, will decativte the old feed, and construct new feed CDT
Update Feed Details will update the neww feed entry detais, and also update the old feed entry details status to false.
